The paper deals with the design and analysis of mechanisms for online marketplaces, which is a topic that falls under the category of game theory (cs.GT). The use of a bidding dashboard also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning techniques. The paper also discusses the implementation of allocation algorithms, which is a topic in both machine learning and optimization (cs.LG and cs.DS). Finally, the paper deals with the economic aspects of online marketplaces, which falls under the category of computational economics (cs.EC).
